<|channel>thought
<channel|># 懵然不知
(pos:形容詞)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知道發生咗咩事，處於一種糊塗或者茫然嘅狀態。
eng:to be completely unaware; to be clueless
<eg>
yue:佢對呢件事完全懵然不知，直到我話俾佢聽先知道。 (keoi5 deoi3 ni1 gin6 si6 jyun4 cyun4 mung2 jin4 bat1 zi1, zi3 dou3 ngo5 waa6 bei2 keoi5 ting1 sin1 zi1 dou6.)
eng:He was completely unaware of this matter until I told him. [end of text]


